# 4. Athena SQL — views de consumo do Glue

## 4.1 Saved queries com hash

```sql
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW ctrl_db.view_md_saved_queries AS
SELECT
    named_query,
    database_name,
    workgroup,
    owner_email,
    description,
    sql_text,
    updated_at,
    md5(regexp_replace(lower(trim(sql_text)), '\\s+', ' ')) AS hash_sql
FROM ctrl_db.catalogo_saved_queries
WHERE sql_text IS NOT NULL;
```

## 4.2 Recent queries filtráveis

```sql
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW ctrl_db.view_md_recent_queries AS
SELECT
    query_execution_id,
    lower(user_email) AS user_email,
    database_name,
    workgroup,
    status,
    sql_text,
    submitted_at,
    completed_at,
    bytes_scanned,
    error_message,
    output_location,
    md5(regexp_replace(lower(trim(sql_text)), '\\s+', ' ')) AS hash_sql
FROM ctrl_db.catalogo_recent_queries
WHERE sql_text IS NOT NULL;
```

